      "date": "2013-08-13 16:56:28.000000000",
      "message": "Patch Set 7: I would prefer that you didn't submit this\n\nI can't see why this patch was made deponent on http://review.whamcloud.com/#/c/7135/7.  If that's not really necessary would prefer to not have the dependency.",
