        "inactive": true
      },
      "date": "2013-08-13 17:08:32.000000000",
      "message": "Patch Set 7:\n\nI see what you are saying, but having the dependencies laid out this way means this patch can't land until #7135 passes.  It seems to me it would make more sense to make this patch independent, then have 3.10 related patches #7135 and #5380 dependent on this patch.  Don't think we should hold up landing pre-3.10 patches on success of 3.10 related patches.",
